\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
体积功
\emph default
: 一定质量气体的准静态膨胀体积
\begin_inset Formula $V_{1}\to V_{2}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A=\int_{V_{1}}^{V_{2}}p\dd V.$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的大小是 
\begin_inset Formula $p-V$
\end_inset

 图中曲线下方面积.
\end_layout

