\begin_layout Itemize
内能和热容: 理想气体
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

仅与
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

有关.
 因此理想气体内能的改变有
\begin_inset Formula $\dd E=\nu C_{V,m}\dd T,\Delta E=\nu C_{V,m}\Delta T.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
定容、定压摩尔热容
\end_layout

